{"id":619920,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/10/【异闻观止】印度两千学生蒙面欢迎习近平/","date":"2019-10-11T12:31:53Z","modified":"2019-10-11T21:57:26Z","title":"【异闻观止】印度两千学生蒙面欢迎习近平","content":"<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>据联合新闻网消息，中国主席习近平今日出访印度，与印度总理莫迪进行会面，而最令人讶异的是，通常他国领导人来访，人民顶多挥舞该国国旗欢迎，但印度清奈（Chennai）一间学校相当“标新立异”，为了欢迎习近平，竟要求两千位学生戴上习近平的面具，并坐在地上排字迎接，画面相当奇特。</p>\n<p>根据NDTV报导，习近平和莫迪选在清奈南方的马马拉普拉姆（Mahabalipuram）地区举办，第二次非正式峰会，负责接待的学校不仅挂出习近平的画布，还派出两千名学生排出“Hearty Welcome”（热烈欢迎）等字迎接，周边的人则负责挥舞印度与中国的国旗，场面相当壮观。</p>\n<p>JU 苹果日报说，香港实施《蒙面法》，港人连戴口罩上街都被警察截查。印度过千学生却被戴上面具，变成“习近平”。国家主席习近平，将今日前往印度，与印度总理莫迪举行第二次非正式峯会。印度新德里电视台（NDTV）报道，当地一间学校为了欢迎习近平到访，竟然要求全校2,000名学生全部戴上习近平面具，又排出“习近平”字样。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-619921\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EGmLcncXkAAkpXG-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"325\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EGmLcncXkAAkpXG-300x195.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EGmLcncXkAAkpXG.jpg 680w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-619922\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EGmLcciW4AQeB5e-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"334\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EGmLcciW4AQeB5e-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EGmLcciW4AQeB5e.jpg 680w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-619923\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EGmLcOjWsAAX-tw-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EGmLcOjWsAAX-tw-300x200.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EGmLcOjWsAAX-tw-768x512.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EGmLcOjWsAAX-tw-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EGmLcOjWsAAX-tw-1080x720.jpg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-619924\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EGmLczWXYAcFJxS-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"347\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EGmLczWXYAcFJxS-300x208.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/EGmLczWXYAcFJxS.jpg 680w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">The Economist called it.</p>\n<p>Though they probably didn’t expect this to happen in India. <a href=\"https://t.co/0mUcwKbHbb\">pic.twitter.com/0mUcwKbHbb</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; ian bremmer (@ianbremmer) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/ianbremmer/status/1182707861211750400?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">October 11, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">这真的不是讽刺禁蒙面法吗？ <a href=\"https://t.co/9dD7PnvNcr\">https://t.co/9dD7PnvNcr</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Chang Ping 长平 (@chang_ping) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/chang_ping/status/1182631209995771904?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">October 11, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\"><b><a title=\"香港反送终示威\" href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%8F%8D%E9%80%81%E7%BB%88%E7%A4%BA%E5%A8%81\">CDS档案 禁蒙面法</a></b></p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-619309 size-thumbnail\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/Anti-mask-lawHK500.3602-150x150.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"150\" height=\"150\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/Anti-mask-lawHK500.3602-150x150.jpg 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/10/Anti-mask-lawHK500.3602-50x50.jpg 50w\"